        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Digital Authenticity for Court Orders Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill generally requires certain court orders, particularly those relating to wiretaps, electronic surveillance, and search and seizures, to have authentic digital signatures.</p>]]>
